<p>I have two sites: <code>index.php</code> and <code>gallery.php</code> I'm including <code>gallery.php</code> via a iframe to <code>index.php</code> In <code>gallery.php</code>, there's a fancy box included. Now it show's the picture in the iframe but i want it to show the picture on the parent window. I've already tried this:</p>  <p><code>gallery.php</code></p>  <pre><code>&lt;?php echo "&lt;a class='fancybox' href=\"$bild\" rel=\"$name\"&gt;&lt;img width=\"200\" src='$bild'/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;"; ?&gt;   &lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt; jQuery(document).ready(function() {  $(".fancybox").click(function() {     parent.$.fancybox();      return false; });    }); &lt;/script&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But if I click on the picture, fancyBox is still loading in the iFrame. What's wrong?</p>